title: Prospect should only be able to view his own profile page
custom_preconds:
GIVEN
The user has logged in as a PROSPECT
e.g. prospect mlbclare+509@gmail.com | Bas3ba11!
custom_steps:
WHEN
Click “Update” on completed profile, the URL displays /prospect//general.
AND now add the number 767: /prospect/767/general

the Prospect should not be directed to view another prospect page.
